<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="bridge-n">bridge <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /brɪdʒ/    美 /brɪdʒ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>桥；桥梁：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>go along / across a bridge 
过桥</p></div>

<h4 id="2-link">2.★ <strong>起桥梁作用的东西；纽带 (link)：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>build a bridge to knowledge
建起通往知识的桥梁</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>桥牌：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>play bridge 
打桥牌</p></div></div>